Create NACC T-Cog Neuropsychological Assessment Summary Table

main_table.Rd

This function create a summary table of measures from the NACC T-Cog Neuropsychological Assessment.

Usage

main_table(dat, bar_height = 16)

Arguments

dat

Data to use. Must have exactly one row (data from one participant and one visit).

bar_height

In pixels. Height of the percentile bars. Default: 16

Value

An object of class gt::gt_tbl

Examples

main_table(
  dat = demo_data[1,]
)
